1. Create your Project Folder
2. Create your index.html file
3. Open your HTML TAG
4. Go to (bootstrapcdn.com/fontawesome)
- <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-wvfXpqpZZVQGK6TAh5PVlGOfQNHSoD2xbE+QkPxCAFlNEevoEH3Sl0sibVcOQVnN" crossorigin="anonymous">
-Copy this link and paste in the html <head></head>
-
5. Create the main div class (this will contain everything in the body tag)
   - create header tag (with an Id= "header" & class = "header")
     . within the header tag (<header></header>), we need a (h1 tag, <h1></h1>)
     . within the header tag and below the (<h1></h1>) , create another div tag to contain the fontawesome icon

     <body>


              <div class="main">
                   <header id="header" class="header">

                       <h1>Shopping Cart</h1>
                       <div class="iconShopping">
                             <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                       </div>

                   </header>
              </div>


     </body>
 6. Now, create CSS File (index.css)
  - create a general setting to control the main page
  *{
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: sans-serif;
  }

    - create main as (absolute)
    - height (10vh)
    - width (100%)
    - display: flex

